# 📌 Project Title
# 🌍 My Travel Footprint — Places You've Been
# Martin Mbuba
A simple JavaScript web application that allows users to track and view all the places they've visited, along with relevant details like location, landmarks, time of year, and notes. This project follows test-driven development (TDD) principles for the core business logic.

