# 📘 About

This web app allows users to keep track of all the places they’ve visited. Users can add destinations, landmarks, time of year, and notes, then search and view them later.

# Features
Add items with multiple properties

Store data in local storage

View item details on click

Search by property (e.g., name or location)

Responsive layout (if applicable)

